         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation" xml:space="preserve"><p>
            <milestone unit="line" n="1"/>To Aurelius Julius Maximus, 
            <app type="BGU"><lem resp="BL I 23."><term target="dekadarches" xml:lang="la">decurio</term></lem></app>,
            <milestone unit="line" n="2" rend="break"/>from Isidora, daughter of Asklas from the village of Karanis. 
            <milestone unit="line" n="3"/>On 12th of the present month Pachon Ptolemaios, son of Ischyras, came up to the 
            house of myself and my brothers, who serve in the army, and stole everything I have, at the 
            value of not less than four hundred <term target="touargurioudrachmai">silver 
                drachmas</term>.
            <milestone unit="line" n="11" rend="break"/>Therefore I submit (this petition) and request that he be brought before 
            you and that I may obtain justice from you.
            <milestone unit="line" n="14" rend="break"/>Farewell.
            <milestone unit="line" n="15" rend="break"/>Year [x – – –].
        </p></div><div type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl/></listBibl></div>
